{"tid":1728825,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實二噁英單嘢，可唔可以迫環保署公布返10月之後嘅數字","createTime":"2019-11-17T04:39:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T05:56:25.000Z","uid":252356,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"46db74bf214e659b3ccc7915b50c9a6f1d35909e","tid":1728825,"uid":252356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:39:02.000Z","msg":"其實二噁英單嘢，可唔可以迫環保署公布返10月之後嘅數字<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rBSUxHd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrBSUxHd.jpg&h=1517d478&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"506cb52448d49109f894bf61574d5a0bcf8a1889","tid":1728825,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T04:47:06.000Z","msg":"他們在打的是「<strong>中共政權保衛戰</strong>」，而你們僅僅是在打「<strong>香港生活方式保衛戰</strong>」<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1728140/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">對付Be Water，第一就是分化，把勇武派、和理非派拆分，第二步是下餌，引誘勇武派進入「必守的陣地」，刺激他們建立碉堡，最好所有的勇武派都集中進入少數陣地（例如四所大學），然後隔絕、撒網、一舉成擒。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（二） 從「誰才是暴徒」辯論陷阱脫身</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">港人對抗港府還算旗鼓相當，畢竟兩邊都是被法治洗禮過的香港人，但是港人對付中共的無底綫宣傳統戰技能，坦白說，還是太嫩。世人關心香港事態的焦點從「港人要自由、要自治」，變成「人民和政府誰才是暴力方」的辯論，這正是北京要製造的焦點轉移。</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">（三） 一切回歸三個字 &ndash; 真普選</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">核心訴求只有一個：真普選，一切口號、行動、宣傳，都環繞真普選這單一訴求展開，這樣，世界聽得懂，連中國內地人民都聽得懂。</span>"},{"pid":"a0f0303bd61b06c7989a6c04db574a96104b81e7","tid":1728825,"uid":252356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a5ef8d62f21db3cad3efe1